      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to believe things can get \"easier\" when the doctors have already told me there's no cure. it feels like i'm just prolonging the inevitable. i look at people who are healthy and moving around and i just feel... empty. like my life is just a cycle of managing pain until i eventually can't anymore. why is it so much harder for some of us to just find peace?",
